  <article class="blog-post">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <header class="blog-hero">
        <div class="blog-hero-image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555396273-367ea4eb4db5?w=1200&h=800&fit=crop" alt="Brentwood restaurants and dining scene" />
        </div>
        <div class="blog-hero-content">
          <h1>Best Date Night Restaurants in Brentwood</h1>
          <p class="blog-subtitle">Discover 4 exclusive romantic dining spots in LA's most refined neighborhood</p>
          <div class="blog-meta">
            <span class="publish-date">Published: October 29, 2025</span>
            <span class="read-time">Reading time: 6 minutes</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <section class="blog-intro">
        <p>Brentwood is one of Los Angeles' most exclusive and refined neighborhoods, known for its elegant atmosphere and sophisticated dining scene. With 4 exceptional date night restaurants, this upscale community offers intimate, high-quality dining experiences perfect for romantic evenings and special celebrations.</p>
        
        <p>Whether you're planning an anniversary dinner, a special date night, or simply want to enjoy a refined dining experience away from the hustle and bustle, Brentwood's carefully curated restaurant scene has something extraordinary for every couple. From authentic Italian trattorias to modern American cuisine, discover the perfect spot for your next romantic dinner in this prestigious neighborhood.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Quick Stats -->
      <section class="blog-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">{brentwoodRestaurants.length}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Restaurants</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">{avgDateScore}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Date Score</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">{upscaleCount}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Upscale Options</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">{cuisineTypes.length}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Cuisine Types</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Top Restaurants -->
      <section class="top-restaurants">
        <h2>Date Night Restaurants in Brentwood</h2>
        <p>These handpicked restaurants offer the perfect combination of romantic ambiance, exceptional cuisine, and memorable experiences for couples.</p>
        
        <div class="restaurants-grid">
          {topRestaurants.map((restaurant, index) => (
            <div class="restaurant-card">
              <div class="restaurant-rank">#{index + 1}</div>
              <h3><a href={`/losangeles/${restaurant.slug}/`}>{restaurant.name}</a></h3>
              <div class="restaurant-details">
                <span class="cuisine">{restaurant.cuisine_types?.join(', ')}</span>
                <span class="price">{'$'.repeat(restaurant.price_level)}</span>
                <span class="date-score">Date Score: {restaurant.date_night_score}</span>
              </div>
              <p class="restaurant-description">{restaurant.description || `A romantic dining experience in Brentwood perfect for date nights.`}</p>
              <a href={`/losangeles/${restaurant.slug}/`} class="btn btn-primary">View Details</a>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Neighborhood Highlights -->
      <section class="neighborhood-highlights">
        <h2>Why Brentwood is Perfect for Date Nights</h2>
        
        <div class="highlights-grid">
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üèõÔ∏è Elegant Atmosphere</h3>
            <p>Brentwood's refined and sophisticated atmosphere creates an ideal setting for romantic dinners, away from the crowds and noise of busier LA neighborhoods.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üç∑ Upscale Dining</h3>
            <p>The neighborhood is known for its high-quality restaurants with excellent wine selections, making it perfect for special occasions and romantic celebrations.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üå≥ Peaceful Ambiance</h3>
            <p>Brentwood's tree-lined streets and quiet atmosphere provide a peaceful backdrop for intimate conversations and memorable date nights.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="highlight-card">
            <h3>üéØ Intimate Settings</h3>
            <p>Smaller, more intimate restaurant spaces ensure a personal and romantic dining experience, perfect for couples seeking quality time together.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Cuisine Diversity -->
      <section class="cuisine-diversity">
        <h2>Culinary Excellence</h2>
        <p>Brentwood's restaurant scene focuses on quality over quantity, featuring carefully curated cuisines:</p>
        
        <ul class="cuisine-list">
          {cuisineTypes.map(cuisine => (
            <li><a href={`/cuisines/${cuisine.toLowerCase().replace(/\s+/g, '-')}/`}>{cuisine.replace(/_/g, ' ')}</a></li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        
        <p>From authentic Italian trattorias to modern American cuisine, each restaurant brings exceptional culinary expertise and attention to detail to create memorable date night experiences.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Planning Your Date Night -->
      <section class="planning-tips">
        <h2>Planning Your Brentwood Date Night</h2>
        
        <div class="tips-grid">
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üïê Best Times to Visit</h3>
            <p>Weekday evenings offer a more intimate and relaxed atmosphere. Weekend nights are perfect for special occasions, and reservations are essential.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üÖøÔ∏è Parking Tips</h3>
            <p>Parking is generally easier than in busier LA neighborhoods. Street parking is available, and many restaurants offer valet service for convenience.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üëó Dress Code</h3>
            <p>Brentwood restaurants lean toward upscale dining. Smart casual to formal attire is appropriate, and some restaurants may have specific dress codes.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="tip-card">
            <h3>üìÖ Reservations</h3>
            <p>Due to the smaller number of restaurants and their popularity, reservations are highly recommended, especially on weekends and for special occasions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Related Content -->
      <section class="related-content">
        <h2>Explore More Date Night Options</h2>
        <div class="related-links">
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/brentwood/" class="related-link">
            <h3>All Brentwood Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Browse our complete list of {brentwoodRestaurants.length} restaurants in Brentwood</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/santa-monica/" class="related-link">
            <h3>Santa Monica Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Discover romantic oceanfront dining in neighboring Santa Monica</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/beverly-hills/" class="related-link">
            <h3>Beverly Hills Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Explore upscale dining in nearby Beverly Hills</p>
          </a>
          
          <a href="/blog/top-anniversary-restaurants-los-angeles/" class="related-link">
            <h3>Anniversary Restaurants</h3>
            <p>Find the perfect spots for special celebrations in LA</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready for Your Next Date Night?</h2>
        <p>With 4 exceptional restaurants to choose from, Brentwood offers intimate and refined dining experiences perfect for couples. Whether you're planning a special celebration or a romantic evening, you're sure to find the perfect spot.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/neighborhoods/brentwood/" class="btn btn-primary">View All Brentwood Restaurants</a>
          <a href="/losangeles/restaurants/" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore All LA Restaurants</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

